snippet.title: Selfloss | Available Now on Steam
snippet.description:
Selfloss is available now on Steam! 🐋

Experience the adventure today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1086620/Selfloss/

Selfloss is an emotional exploration game filled with rich lore, set in a whale-worshipping, Slavic-inspired world. Embark on the journey of the healer, Kazimir, and his magical staff as he fights a mysterious Miasma in search of a ritual to cure his wounded soul.

Selfloss comes to PS5, Xbox Series X|S and Nintendo Switch on September 12 - add the game to your wishlist today!

Follow Selfloss on social media and wishlist now: https://linktr.ee/selfloss
